
= MoDi

URL = https://www.monetarydiversity.org/about-modi


=Description=

"MoDi is an initiative aimed at promoting complementary and alternative monetary systems and experimentations for social, environmental and economic purposes to better fulfil monetary functions for society. We advocate a more comprehensive and open legal framework for the democratization and the open development of complementary payment media towards policymakers and the general public."


